				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Melee getting weak.....<a name="5689"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 25 03 12:23 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>At lvl 41 I find I can outdamage my two best swords with just my two chants and a Tamborine of Rituals.  As much as I love to stand back and destroy from afar when in a group, I feel guilty that my melee skills have dropped of so much lately.  Between charming &amp; swarm-kiting I rarely have to wipe the blood from my blades.
<br />

<br />
I know that you will tell me to always keep up my melee skills but do all you 50+ folks keep them maxxed?  My 1hs and 1hb blunts are about 180/165 somewhere.  Should I bite some blades and get them maxxed out or is there sort of a happy medium now that instruments seem to work better than weapons?
<br />

<br />
All opinions are welcome</span></td>
