				<td colspan="2"><span>Melee lacking??
<br />

<br />
Ok, my weapon skills are all mexxed, tho at every level 1hp is the last one to get maxxed.  I tend to group a lot, and my melee dps aint too shabby, in fact, I'd go as far to say thats its at least as good as some of the pallys I group with, if not higher, I hit for 60's-90's and it for that much quite regularly.  My guess is that some bards lack balance, and focus on dex and cha far too much and let other stats lag.  I have about 140 in every stat, except wis and int, which are around 105, and have 36% item haste. Sure I miss a few more notes or have a few more reists, but its not all that noticable, but my melee output is <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" />.  Bards are not inherantly bad at melee, but gear and choice of item hastes and stat-focus does affect melee ablility quite a bit.</span></td>
